# FluentES -  Elasticsearch Fluent Query Builder

A small Python library for building Elasticsearch queries using a fluent API.

Example:
```python
from fluentes import QueryBuilder

q = (
    QueryBuilder()
    .match("title", "python")
    .term("status", "active")
    .build()
)

print(q)
```

